{"tid":1420732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與其搞記招，不如派報紙對抗柒婆抹黑","createTime":"2019-08-06T05:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T15:50:39.000Z","uid":292798,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6adc9c164e046e536c8a88e72dd2d8dc9c364011","tid":1420732,"uid":292798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"柒婆搞抹黑，我地搞洗白係梗<br />\n但記招我地無可能日日準備充足，到時實有啲19記者問啲答唔到嘅問題，又畀位人入<br />\n我覺得單向洗白就好，廢時講多錯多<br />\n班狗官古惑我地更加要古惑過佢地<br />\n以牙還牙先係大道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點樣派？地鐵站又好，屋企電梯大堂又好<br />\n甚至好似之前咁長老圖airdrop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實行做進擊的連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4d87bec0ad16a44d648a3cdd2f321b306c3cdb","tid":1420732,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />pish"},{"pid":"9e93fe5701a69c9d8d086c932d430fd002e4eb67","tid":1420732,"uid":238688,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"6adc9c164e046e536c8a88e72dd2d8dc9c364011","tid":1420732,"uid":292798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"柒婆搞抹黑，我地搞洗白係梗<br />\n但記招我地無可能日日準備充足，到時實有啲19記者問啲答唔到嘅問題，又畀位人入<br />\n我覺得單向洗白就好，廢時講多錯多<br />\n班狗官古惑我地更加要古惑過佢地<br />\n以牙還牙先係大道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點樣派？地鐵站又好，屋企電梯大堂又好<br />\n甚至好似之前咁長老圖airdrop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實行做進擊的連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:40:00.000Z","msg":"why not both? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9301d4e5a117ad2afbb2b60e5c5e13d8e9aac73","tid":1420732,"uid":287015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:42:32.000Z","msg":"揾文宣幫手<br />\n整合記者會內容<br />\n再整圖貼牆/airdrop/派？"},{"pid":"8c4c335e313b9ce6ced756aacd518f30503974a6","tid":1420732,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:43:43.000Z","msg":"呢個時代仲有咩人會睇報紙"},{"pid":"58ed6bb00a80bbcb0d9403ec5720e885282d1d97","tid":1420732,"uid":292798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c4c335e313b9ce6ced756aacd518f30503974a6","tid":1420732,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:43:43.000Z","msg":"呢個時代仲有咩人會睇報紙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:49:34.000Z","msg":"姐係咁樣講易明，同埋免費報紙好多人攞"},{"pid":"c5c0313936ed513c4ab90e1354a93fc33812b444","tid":1420732,"uid":148759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:49:34.000Z","msg":"一般港豬鍾意聽八卦野 我地可唔可以喺柒婆同黑勢力勾結呢點上面做文章？"},{"pid":"332ec4f3faf1e0d244baabdf17ae5a65f5799377","tid":1420732,"uid":292798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9301d4e5a117ad2afbb2b60e5c5e13d8e9aac73","tid":1420732,"uid":287015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:42:32.000Z","msg":"揾文宣幫手<br />\n整合記者會內容<br />\n再整圖貼牆/airdrop/派？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:50:13.000Z","msg":"三方一齊做都得，醬汁都係一樣"},{"pid":"fe8de1e0593abde324ae7f60f43ba126857ba48a","tid":1420732,"uid":292798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e93fe5701a69c9d8d086c932d430fd002e4eb67","tid":1420732,"uid":238688,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"6adc9c164e046e536c8a88e72dd2d8dc9c364011","tid":1420732,"uid":292798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"柒婆搞抹黑，我地搞洗白係梗<br />\n但記招我地無可能日日準備充足，到時實有啲19記者問啲答唔到嘅問題，又畀位人入<br />\n我覺得單向洗白就好，廢時講多錯多<br />\n班狗官古惑我地更加要古惑過佢地<br />\n以牙還牙先係大道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點樣派？地鐵站又好，屋企電梯大堂又好<br />\n甚至好似之前咁長老圖airdrop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實行做進擊的連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:40:00.000Z","msg":"why not both? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"Both就係怕記者會好易犯錯，而家係鬥犯錯少<br />\n邊個少錯就贏了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c1b78c58fe4264995333248d58902a1769bbac","tid":1420732,"uid":202577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:54:49.000Z","msg":"老實講我覺得記招，作用大，風險小。始終係公眾傳媒，一次過多d人體。<br />\n只不過要面對記者，但就算d問題有心刁難，多可以靠我地一齊思考搞掂。太過離譜嘅問題，又可以一笑置之，例如解放軍果條咁。<br />\n連儂牆一樣要面對困難，班廢老可能打完人唔使坐監。<br />\n由連儂牆到記招，我覺得係一大進步。"},{"pid":"d53bb9c2de9a1fde7a8a6d3b167a5bf181fe13f5","tid":1420732,"uid":292798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:54:57.000Z","msg":"做記者會要等齊腳，又有時效性<br />\nairdrop只要批好份文宣就可以周圍射無限射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c58b9ed2758a34db84e5d9ff2b97dce0931a81e","tid":1420732,"uid":292798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2c1b78c58fe4264995333248d58902a1769bbac","tid":1420732,"uid":202577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:54:49.000Z","msg":"老實講我覺得記招，作用大，風險小。始終係公眾傳媒，一次過多d人體。<br />\n只不過要面對記者，但就算d問題有心刁難，多可以靠我地一齊思考搞掂。太過離譜嘅問題，又可以一笑置之，例如解放軍果條咁。<br />\n連儂牆一樣要面對困難，班廢老可能打完人唔使坐監。<br />\n由連儂牆到記招，我覺得係一大進步。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:56:25.000Z","msg":"記招個即時性我地根本幫唔到，唔通次次都話我下次答你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有要答問題嘅根本係正苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6778e71a226911373616cea9e780713e86d52262","tid":1420732,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:04:47.000Z","msg":"可以一齊做。<br />\n班染紅記者嘅策略都係話個記招無代表性<br />\n可以問翻個記者：如果你見到鄰居被流氓虐打，但無人處理，咁你將件事講翻出黎，有乜問題？件事發生咗就發生咗。"},{"pid":"5e38de1634bad476b3bf438c6606e889c3aa0575","tid":1420732,"uid":292798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6778e71a226911373616cea9e780713e86d52262","tid":1420732,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:04:47.000Z","msg":"可以一齊做。<br />\n班染紅記者嘅策略都係話個記招無代表性<br />\n可以問翻個記者：如果你見到鄰居被流氓虐打，但無人處理，咁你將件事講翻出黎，有乜問題？件事發生咗就發生咗。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:17:00.000Z","msg":"都係果句，記招容易犯錯<br />\n更加容易曝露手足身份，啲狗識跟蹤人嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c0994cf0794